ComicInfo.Summary:
THE CONCLUSION OF "ANIMAL HOUSE," A CROSSOVER WITH THE UNBEATABLE SQUIRREL GIRL!
WATCH! Howard show Squirrel Girl how to be a REAL hero for a change, for which she is eternally grateful!
LEARN! what happened in last month's UNBEATABLE SQUIRREL GIRL #6 from the recap page!
LISTEN! to a nice audio file of nature sounds made by Chip & Ryan while you read this VERY good story!
LOVE! all the guest stars! Like one of the blue guys from X-MEN! And a pretty cool van!
